(52170,NULL,2,'sys.doc.richtext','<p class=\"MsoNormal\">会员登录信息<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>登录过的设备列表<span lang=\"EN-US\">,IP</span>列表<span lang=\"EN-US\"> (ES</span>的 <span lang=\"EN-US\">/member_login_log_2019_08)<span>&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></span>曾用名<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>名字不变的<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">游戏记录信息<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>&nbsp;\n</span></span>以及游戏记录的 统计信息 <span lang=\"EN-US\">(ES</span>中 <span lang=\"EN-US\">/game_record_2019_07\n<span>&nbsp;</span>validBetAmount</span>有效投注<span lang=\"EN-US\">, netAmount</span>盈亏<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">会员存款流水<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>最近<span lang=\"EN-US\">90</span>天在当前亚博库<span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span>超过<span lang=\"EN-US\">90</span>天在亚博归档库<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">会员基本信息<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>包括标签（<span lang=\"EN-US\">member_tags</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">tags</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>余额<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>中心账户<span lang=\"EN-US\">members.money, </span>场馆余额<span lang=\"EN-US\">members_api.money);<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">会员存款流水<span lang=\"EN-US\">(recharge),<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>90</span>天内有无存款记录<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><span style=\"font-family: consolas, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">在线状态 (DB中没有，咨询后端开发)</span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</o:p></span>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span>http://39.108.249.134:56010/app/kibana#/discover?_g=()&amp;_a=(columns:!(_source),index:e052cbc0-80b1-11e9-807c-e7733624f205,interval:auto,query:(language:lucene,query:\'\'),sort:!(\'@timestamp\',desc))</p